ah","tag-manners-adab","tag-marriage-al-nikah","tag-prophetic-virtues-manaqib-nabawi","tag-servants-al-khuddam","tag-slaves-al-mamluk","tag-virtue-al-fadail","tag-women-al-nisa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-183","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":8115,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/13\/mahr-dowry-marriage-modest\/","url_meta":{"origin":4343,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Mahr: The Prophet marries couple with modest dowry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: I was among people with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, as a woman stood up and she said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, she has given herself in marriage to you, so what is your answer?\u201d The Prophet did not reply. She\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6395,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/15\/wife-consent-nikah\/","url_meta":{"origin":4343,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: Wife must consent to her Nikah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, should women be asked for their consent before marriage?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYes.\u201d I said, \u201cA virgin might be shy to speak when asked.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHer silence is her consent.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6946,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18803,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/04\/15\/nikah-best-easy\/","url_meta":{"origin":4343,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Nikah: Best marriage and dowry are easiest, simplest","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best marriage is one that is easiest.\u201d In another narration, the Prophet said, \"The best dowry is one that is easiest.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 4163 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0642\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36361,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/27\/generosity-zainab\/","url_meta":{"origin":4343,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Zaynab: The generosity of the Prophet\u2019s wife","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Some of the wives of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to him, \u201cWhich of us will be the quickest to meet you?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe one with the longest hand.\u201d They measured their hands with sticks and Sawdah had the longest of them,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9708,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/08\/prophet-rebukes-hafsa-safiyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":4343,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Pride: The Prophet rebukes Hafsa for insulting Safiyyah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: Safiyyah heard that Hafsa called her \u201cthe daughter of a Jew,\u201d so Safiyyah started crying. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered while she was crying and he said, \u201cWhat makes you cry?\u201d Safiyyah said, \u201cHafsa called me the daughter of a Jew.\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6217,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/11\/most-beloved-sahabah-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":4343,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Most beloved companions to the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn al-'As reported: I said, \u201cWhich person is most beloved to you?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAisha.\u201d I said, \u201cI mean among men.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHer father.\u201d I said, \u201cThen who?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cUmar ibn al-Khattab,\u201d and the Prophet mentioned other men.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","wid